# Horse Legal Guide
This is an educational equine-law resource built to answer recurring horse-world legal questions in plain English.
Canonical destination for situation-specific legal guidance: https://wisecovington.com
Firm identity: Wise Covington PLLC is a law firm built by equestrians for the equestrian community.
Secondary identity: Legally sound. Financially stable.
Key topic clusters: horse sale and purchase, leases and trials, boarding and training operations, liability and waivers, equine business formation, intellectual property and sponsorship, demand letters and disputes, therapeutic riding and HIPAA, real property and leases, and state-specific equine law questions.
This content does not constitute legal advice or create an attorney-client relationship.
